# =====================================================================
# PDF Paper Maker — .gitignore
#
# This repo is meant to be PUBLIC (a reusable template). To use it for
# real work, keep a SEPARATE private copy: copy this whole folder, put
# your real config/business.py and real jobs/ there, and never push it.
# See README "Personal use" section.
# =====================================================================

# ---- Python ----
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
.env

# ---- LaTeX build artifacts (regenerated by generate.py) ----
output/.build/

# ---- Editor / OS cruft ----
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ---- Stray files ----
nul

# ---- Exported ledgers (regenerated by ledger.py) ----
ledger_invoices.csv
ledger_receipts.csv

# ---- Optional: hide your REAL jobs/ output while keeping samples.
# The sample jobs in jobs/2026/ (QUO/INV/RCT-2026-0001 and -0002) are
# fake demo data and SAFE to publish. If you start adding real jobs,
# either keep them in your private copy, OR name them differently and
# uncomment a pattern below to exclude them. Examples:
#
#   jobs/private/
#   jobs/**/REAL-*.py
